@startuml AI Goal Layer Diagram For Portfolio
title AI Goal Layer Diagram
top to bottom direction
package "AI" #DDDDDD
{  
  package "Goal Layer" #DDDDDD
  {
    class GoalBehaviourControllerSO <<ScriptableObject>>

    class Idle <<GoalBehaviourControllerSO>>
    class AttackNearestEnemy <<GoalBehaviourControllerSO>>
    class FollowPlayerInFormation<<GoalBehaviourControllerSO>>

    GoalBehaviourControllerSO -[hidden]-> Idle
    GoalBehaviourControllerSO -[hidden]-> AttackNearestEnemy
    GoalBehaviourControllerSO -[hidden]-> FollowPlayerInFormation

    note top of GoalBehaviourControllerSO
    GoalBehaviourControllerSO is running
    step behaviour controllers responsible
    for running actions/steps, that are
    required to reach the "goal"
    of the goal behaviour.
    end note

    note left of GoalBehaviourControllerSO
    Idle, AttackNearestEnemy and
    FollowPlayerInFormation
    inherit this base class.
    end note

    note right of GoalBehaviourControllerSO
    It holds all step behaviour controllers
    responsible for running actions required
    to reach the goal of the behaviour.
    end note
  }

  note "Do Nothing" as N1
  note "Attack Enemies" as N2
  note "Follow Player" as N3

  package "Step/Action Layer" #DDDDDD
  {
    class DoNothing <<StepBehaviourControllerSO>>
    class TryToAttackNearestEnemy <<StepBehaviourControllerSO>>
    class TryToFollowPlayerInFormation <<StepBehaviourControllerSO>>

    Idle --> N1
    N1 --> DoNothing

    AttackNearestEnemy --> N2
    N2 --> TryToAttackNearestEnemy

    FollowPlayerInFormation --> N3
    N3 --> TryToFollowPlayerInFormation
  }
}
@enduml